data.description:
A new take on our 1st Imperial IPA; massively hopped w/ columbus, chinook, simcoe & 
centennial hops, then dry-hopped with cascade, centennial, columbus & simcoe; 
deliciously dank with aromas of resinous pine, freshly picked flowers, & citrus fruit.

